    "This is how Ramírez explained to me the differences between the local communities and a delegation from the German government interested in increasing lithium extraction:",
    "The final objective of Germany is to make this extraction sustainable.",
    "In other words, to take charge of the whole value chain.",
    "But in this value chain, the main feature is water extraction.",
    "No solution is provided for that."
